Agents for Visual Studio 2015 Update 3 (x86 and x64) - (Japanese)
Files.Notes:
This update is the latest in a cumulative series of feature additions and bug fixes for Agents for Visual Studio 2015.

Use Agents for Visual Studio 2015 Update 3 for distributing automated tests across multiple remote machines for continuous testing in Team Build or Release Management pipelines. The agent package can be downloaded, installed, and configured using the ‘Visual Studio Test Agent Deployment’ task from the task catalog. Couple this with the ‘Run Functional Tests’ task for running tests and collecting diagnostic data such as code coverage.

Agents for Visual Studio 2015 Update 3 cannot be used for running load tests, running functional tests in the XAML build workflows, running automated tests using Microsoft Test Manager (MTM) or for managing lab environments using Visual Studio Lab Management.

For these scenarios, please use Agents for Visual Studio 2013 Update 5.
